rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0001
rows.name:
...There's no reason I should recognize
this place...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0002
rows.name: So what is this I feel...?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0003
rows.name:
This tugging in my breast...
I can't shake this sense of...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0004
rows.name: Musubi?!

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0005
rows.name: You're Musubi, aren't you?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0006
rows.name: Hm?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0007
rows.name: So you've come back!

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0008
rows.name: Daddy'd be so happy...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0009
rows.name:
...Oh, um...
Who might you be?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0010
rows.name: Huh?!

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0011
rows.name:
What're you talking about?
Don't you recognize us?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0012
rows.name: Musubi doesn't remember any more.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0013
rows.name: Musubi's not got memories from before.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0014
rows.name: Musubi doesn't remember her past.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0015
rows.name: Musubi's forgotten her old life.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0016
rows.name:
I see... So Musubi's memories got
wiped after Daddy passed away...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0017
rows.name: And so you're her new Driver now?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0018
rows.name:
Oh, yeah.
The old man, well, entrusted her to us...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0019
rows.name:
Right. You could say the old man
left her to us...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0020
rows.name: Yes, indeed.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0021
rows.name: Mhm, right.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0022
rows.name:
Well then, it's a relief that
her new Driver is a nice person.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0023
rows.name:
It's nice. Daddy would be happy
knowing you're taking care of her.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0024
rows.name: You two are...?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0025
rows.name: You belong to this household, right?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0026
rows.name: You knew my old self?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0101
rows.name:
This is the house our daddy used to
live in.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0102
rows.name:
But just the other day, he
moved on from this life...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0103
rows.name:
We haven't been back in a while,
but we needed to make arrangements...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0104
rows.name: Ah, I see. I'm sorry for your loss...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0105
rows.name: Can I help you in any way?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0106
rows.name:
No, but I really appreciate you
saying that.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0107
rows.name:
May I ask though, why did you
come here?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0108
rows.name:
That's...
I couldn't really tell you.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0109
rows.name:
But when I saw this house, I felt a
warm wash of nostalgia...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0110
rows.name: Is that right...?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0111
rows.name:
I think whoever lived here
must have been a great person.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0112
rows.name: Why do you say that?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0113
rows.name:
Well, I...know it from looking at
you two.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0114
rows.name:
After all, he raised a pair of wonderful
children like you.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0115
rows.name: It's the sure mark of a great person.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0116
rows.name: ...No, our daddy was just a regular guy.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0117
rows.name:
The real great person here was the
one who raised us after our ma died.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0118
rows.name: Kinder and warmer than Ma ever was...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0119
rows.name: Where is that person now?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0120
rows.name:
...Taking care of important business,
I hear.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0121
rows.name:
But we hope to meet them again,
once that's done.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0122
rows.name: We'll have so much to talk about.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0123
rows.name:
I see.
Well, I think that's good.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0124
rows.name: I'm sure they will be happy to.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0201
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0202
rows.name: We owe you a lot, from before.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0203
rows.name: I'm glad I was able to meet you.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0204
rows.name: That's nice...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0205
rows.name:
So before my latest awakening,
this is where I lived...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0206
rows.name: So, whose house is this?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0207
rows.name:
It belongs to our daddy.
But he passed away recently...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0208
rows.name:
...So your father
would have known me, right?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0209
rows.name: Daddy didn't just know you.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0210
rows.name:
He relied on you for
pretty much everything.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0211
rows.name:
I think he'd be happy you came today.
Wherever he is now...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0212
rows.name:
Ah, I'm sorry if I offend.
I don't have any memory of that time...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0213
rows.name: I'm sorry about everything.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0214
rows.name:
It's fine, Musubi.
Please, think no more of it.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0215
rows.name:
We're very happy you came today,
regardless.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0216
rows.name:
I almost forgot!
Here, dumplings.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0217
rows.name:
They may not be the best
of offerings, but, well...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0218
rows.name:
In any case, they're freshly made.
Please, help yourselves.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0219
rows.name: ...Dumplings...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0220
rows.name: It's been a while...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0221
rows.name:
I may have no memories,
but this is the least I can do...

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0222
rows.name:
Not at all.
This is perfect. Thank you.

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0223
rows.name:
Um... Would you mind terribly if I
visited again sometime...?

rows.label: kizunatalk073_msg0224
rows.name:
Of course we wouldn't mind!
This is your home too, after all.
